&lt;p&gt;We are a modern and innovative Podiatry Service in inner London providing a comprehensive range of foot health services to a diverse community. We currently have a vacancy for a motivated individual at band 6 level, with an interest in wound care&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We provide regular protected learning time, encouraging all podiatrists to develop their clinical and professional skills as part of their personal development plan, with access to post graduate training &amp; development.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If you are a highly motivated Podiatrist who would like the opportunity to develop their clinical skills and career opportunities, then we would like to give you the opportunity to join our team by inviting you to apply for this post.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
